<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Albrecht von Wertheim, Bischof von Bamberg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Heinrich Huber, Diener der Stadt, und Kathrin Hetzelsdorfer, Bürgerin zu Nürnberg, wegen ihres Streits mit Erasmus von Wiesenthau über die vom Adressaten zu Lehen rührenden Güter ihres verstorbenen Ehemanns Hermann an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_279" id="139v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_279_r1l1">Byſſchoff cʒu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_279_r1l2"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> herre . Vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> fraw kathrey die <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> hecʒelſtorfferin </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l3"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burgerin . vvie ſie Eraſm von wyſentaw . an <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> dıe Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l4"><expan>egen<ex>enanter</ex></expan> ~ vvirt ſelig von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>cʒuleh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gehabt hab . vnd dıe ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l5">gnade Jr vormals cʒu <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ Jrem wirte <expan>verlıh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab irre vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l6">enge vnd Jr einfelle darein mache darümb ſie <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l7">gnaden cʒekumen . vnd das <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden ſelber auch cʒuercʒelen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l8">maint . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burgerin darynne </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l9">
<del rend="strikethrough">durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></del> <expan>gnaͤdiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein laſſen 
<del rend="strikethrough"> wöllet </del> vnd Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l10">ewr gnade vnd <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> beweiſen wöllet / vnd waʒ auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l11"><expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> huber <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> diener in <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache cʒu dıſem mal an </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l12">ewr gnade werbend ſey von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen . des wöllet Jm <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l13">vnd darynne durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> tun Als etc Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_279" id="139v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bysschoff czu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> herre, uns hat
                            <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> fraw Kathrey, die
                            <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Heczelstorfferin,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burgerin, wie sie Erasm von Wysentaw an
                                <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan>, die ir <expan>egen<ex>enanter</ex></expan>
                        wirt, selig, von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>czu leh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gehabt hab und die ewr gnade ir vormals
                        czu <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> irem wirte
                            <expan>verlih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab, irre und enge und ir einfelle
                        darein mache, darümb sie <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden cze kumen und das
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden selber auch czu erczelen maint.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        gnaden <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burgerin darynne
                            <expan>gnaͤdiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lassen und ir ewr gnade und
                                <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> beweisen wöllet, und waz auch
                                <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Huber,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener, in
                            <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache czu disem mal an ewr gnade
                        werbend sey von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen, des wöllet im
                                <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und darynne durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> tun, als etc. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
